Cairo Photography Club was founded in 2011 Our idea was to build a community for photographers where they can learn, Practice and improve their skills, also to offer activities, workshops and outing to allow photographers to practice and improve their photography skills and encourage them to bring their best. Later, we started improving and adding more sections to our club to provide more integrated services to photographers to cover all their photography needs to become the photographer they want to be.
